{"type": "article", "id": 20559, "title": "皮质储物盒", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-12T07:13:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606150259tAFEHBrWx4yT3h5Y.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t储物盒通常采用塑料、木头或者金属等坚硬的材料，看似柔软的皮革也有细腻的手工感。这套皮质的储物盒上没有任何花纹或点缀，对应两侧有编织的痕迹，可以清晰看到皮革本身的纹路，很有触感。它与通常文具所使用的材料也是不同的，放在桌面上给人眼前一亮的感受，有红、黄、黑三种颜色的三种型号，<a href=\"http://www.munito.co.kr/product/detail.html?product_no=102&amp;cate_no=1&amp;display_group=3\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061502576qzldkmJxhuytsnV.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6647619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150258NwKD09vIciHRY3qE.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6647619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150258W945EqZ20UfbyHRu.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6647619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150259Q1YUElozvMwbe48p.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6647619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}